# Workspace rules (non-negotiable)

1. If `STATE.md` does not exist in the project root, stop and run the
   bootstrap skill (`.cursor/skills/bootstrap-workspace/SKILL.md`)
   before doing anything else. Do not create or edit other files first.

2. Otherwise, read `AGENTS.md` in the project root and follow its
   rules. AGENTS.md is the canonical source for workspace structure,
   the knowledge layer (STATE.md plus optional IDENTITY.md and
   VISION.md), the working-file persistence layer (`_working/`),
   consolidation, auditing, and markdown conventions. Re-read it when
   in doubt rather than guessing.
